@process{syslog} (actually @sc{rsyslog}: see @code{man rsyslogd (8)})
is used by all @activity{mediatex}'s binaries and scripts.

3 environment variables manage the content to log:
@table @code
@item MDTX_LOG_FACILITY
@item MDTX_LOG_FILE
@item MDTX_LOG_SEVERITY
@end table
These variables are overwritten when using the corresponding command line options (@xref{Options}).

